Xrjw">Trúc chi ca kỳ 04 - 竹枝歌其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/U%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/author-HbKyCtS3WFreEebdROalkQ">Uông Nguyên Lượng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%B1-kinh-ph%C3%B3-Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-Ti%C3%AAn-huy%E1%BB%87n-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-ng%C5%A9-b%C3%A1ch-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-qHlDll4qtUH2nCJy2-kR4Q">Tự kinh phó Phụng Tiên huyện vịnh hoài ngũ bách tự - 自京赴奉先縣詠懷五百字</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A7n-Qu%C3%A1n/V%E1%BB%8Dng-h%E1%BA%A3i-tri%E1%BB%81u/poem-YIwnMWpZcmUiNqaZPntoJQ">Vọng hải triều - 望海潮</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A7n-Qu%C3%A1n/author-Ahda3BBxTRNmdfIe5Q5e-Q">Tần Quán</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Hu%E1%BB%B3nh-Th%C3%BAc-Kh%C3%A1ng/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-WY374ZRcTyYdeZO__ePAtg">Vô đề kỳ 2 - 無題其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Hu%E1%BB%B3nh-Th%C3%BAc-Kh%C3%A1ng/author-tWIJ_JcBg9FILAgkriOf3g">Huỳnh Thúc Kháng</a>)<br></div>	</div>
